{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/PROJECT/bootstrap-with-tailwind/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jwhy Blogitory","author":"[Jwhy]","siteUrl":"https://jwhyee.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"Jwhyee/Jwhyee.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jwhy"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eea7ada1-ff9d-5e6c-bcf1-5f031ae8ad3f","excerpt":"사건 발달 해커톤 프로젝트 진행을 위해 팀원들과 함께 템플릿을 구매하여 개발을 진행하고 있었다.\n해당 템플릿은  기반이라 사용하다보니 와  등의 문제로 결국 를 함께 사용해야겠다는 생각이 들어 진행했다. 프로젝트 상태 intelliJ IDEA 사용\nSpringBoot + bootstrap 기반의 5인 개발 프로젝트 현재 아래와 같이  방식으로 을 가져와 사용 중이다. 적용 방법 적용 방법은 정말 친절하게도 tailwind…","html":"<h2 id=\"사건-발달\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EA%B1%B4-%EB%B0%9C%EB%8B%AC\" aria-label=\"사건 발달 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사건 발달</h2>\n<p>해커톤 프로젝트 진행을 위해 팀원들과 함께 템플릿을 구매하여 개발을 진행하고 있었다.\n해당 템플릿은 <code class=\"language-text\">bootstrap</code> 기반이라 사용하다보니 <code class=\"language-text\">width</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">background-color</code> 등의 문제로 결국 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind</code>를 함께 사용해야겠다는 생각이 들어 진행했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-상태\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 상태 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 상태</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>intelliJ IDEA 사용<br>\nSpringBoot + bootstrap 기반의 5인 개발 프로젝트</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>현재 아래와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">cdn</code> 방식으로 <code class=\"language-text\">bootstrap</code>을 가져와 사용 중이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Bootstrap CSS --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"적용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"적용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용 방법</h2>\n<p>적용 방법은 정말 친절하게도 <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation\">tailwind</a> 공식 문서에 잘 나와있다.<br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>현재 프로젝트에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">.gitignore</code> 에 <code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>를 추가해놨기 때문에, 모든 팀원이 아래 방식을 같이 진행했다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"1-tawindcss-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-tawindcss-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 tawindcss 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. tawindcss 설치</h3>\n<p>우선 아래 순서대로 프로젝트 터미널에서 명령어를 입력해준다.<br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -D tailwindcss\nnpx tailwindcss init</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 534px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"npm npx install\"\n        title=\"npm npx install\"\n        src=\"/static/549f13d23f90f2d68a744157b90a4118/a07a7/npm-npx-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/549f13d23f90f2d68a744157b90a4118/5a46d/npm-npx-install.png 300w,\n/static/549f13d23f90f2d68a744157b90a4118/a07a7/npm-npx-install.png 534w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>설치가 완료되면 프로젝트에 <code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code> 폴더와 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind.config.js</code>가 추가된 것을 볼 수 있을 것이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-tailwindconfigjs-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-tailwindconfigjs-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 tailwindconfigjs 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. tailwind.config.js 수정</h3>\n<p>config 파일 내용을 아래와 같이 수정해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  prefix<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'tw-'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  content<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'./src/main/**/*.{html,js}'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'./src/main/**/*'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/*theme: {\n    extend: {},\n  },\n  plugins: [],*/</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-base-css-파일-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-base-css-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 base css 파일 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. base CSS 파일 수정</h3>\n<p>프로젝트에 가장 기본이 되는 <code class=\"language-text\">CSS</code> 파일이 하나씩은 존재할것이다.<br>\n만약 그런 <code class=\"language-text\">CSS</code> 파일이 없다면 아래와 같은 경로에 비어있는 <code class=\"language-text\">style.css</code> 파일을 생성해준다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>사실 어떤 CSS 파일이어도 상관 없지만, 애매하면 새로 만드는 것이 좋다.<br></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">./src/main/resources/static/style.css</code></pre></div>\n<p>다음으로 기존에 있던 CSS 파일에 아래와 같은 <code class=\"language-text\">at-rules(어노테이션)</code> 을 추가해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> components<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@tailwind</span> utilities<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>아마 <code class=\"language-text\">intelliJ</code> 에서는 빨간색 줄이 뜰텐데 아무 문제 없으니 걱정말자!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"4-build\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-build\" aria-label=\"4 build permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. build</h3>\n<p>위 과정을 그대로 새로 style.css를 추가했다면 아래와 같은 명령어를 입력해주면 되고,\n그게 아니라면 본인이 해당 어노테이션을 추가한 파일의 이름과 경로를 맞게 입력해주면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">npx tailwindcss -i ./src/main/resources/static/style.css -o ./src/main/resources/static/dist/output.css --watch</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.333333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAjElEQVQI12PQUtf+b+ae+t85oee/c1z7f4/UiUA86b9bUu9/18RuMHZJ6PpvH9v5v7gg639XVcz/sACf/3IKJv/VNSz+q6oDsZr5f2UV0/9Kysb/GdQ1rf5r69j9V1Ex+a+pZfVfV88eiO1QaC1ta7C8lo79f209x/86QKxv6Pxfz8AJjEFskBkaQLMAbC1GKyLYCVQAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output ex\"\n        title=\"output ex\"\n        src=\"/static/9671d5e382d9f98f4efe8a39c844c5e8/5a190/output-ex.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9671d5e382d9f98f4efe8a39c844c5e8/5a46d/output-ex.png 300w,\n/static/9671d5e382d9f98f4efe8a39c844c5e8/0a47e/output-ex.png 600w,\n/static/9671d5e382d9f98f4efe8a39c844c5e8/5a190/output-ex.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>❌  주의할 점 ❌ <br>\n위 과정을 마치면 아래 와 같은 코드가 나올 것이다. 여기서 <code class=\"language-text\">controll + c</code> 로 나가지 않고 그대로 둔다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">Rebuilding<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\nDone <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> 191ms.</code></pre></div>\n<p>이와같이 진행하면 아래와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">dist</code> 폴더 안에 <code class=\"language-text\">output.css</code> 가 생겼을 것이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 356px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dist output\"\n        title=\"dist output\"\n        src=\"/static/587ea48bb3ff9438bbadffa33824ba53/50ac3/dist-output.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/587ea48bb3ff9438bbadffa33824ba53/5a46d/dist-output.png 300w,\n/static/587ea48bb3ff9438bbadffa33824ba53/50ac3/dist-output.png 356w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 356px) 100vw, 356px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"5-바꿔-넣기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%94-%EB%84%A3%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"5 바꿔 넣기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 바꿔 넣기</h3>\n<p>마지막으로 <code class=\"language-text\">layout</code> 혹은 <code class=\"language-text\">fragments</code> 에 넣어놨던 코드를 <code class=\"language-text\">output.css</code> 로 바꿔준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    ...\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 기존에 사용하던 CSS --></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- &lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" th:href=\"@{/style.css}\">  --></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 새로 output된 CSS --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/dist/output.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>만약 <code class=\"language-text\">layout</code> 혹은 <code class=\"language-text\">fragments</code>를 사용하지 않고 모든 페이지마다 <code class=\"language-text\">head</code>를 넣어줬다면\n유감스럽게도 모든 <code class=\"language-text\">html</code> 파일에 적용해줘야한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"6-사용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"6 사용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 사용</h3>\n<p>아까 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind.config.js</code>를 수정할 때 미리 눈치챘을 수 있겠지만, <code class=\"language-text\">prefix: 'tw-'</code>를 넣어준 이유는 이미 <code class=\"language-text\">bootstrap</code>이 프로젝트의 주된 라이브러리로 자리를 잡고 있기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind</code>의 <code class=\"language-text\">class</code> 명과 헷갈리지 않기 위해 넣어줬다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>input-group tw-bg-blue-500<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>select</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form-select<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sortCode<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>NEWEST<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>selected</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${sortCode} == <span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>NEWEST<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>최신순<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>OLDEST<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>selected</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${sortCode} == <span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>OLDEST<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>오래된순<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind</code>의 클래스 문법 앞에 <code class=\"language-text\">tw-</code> 를 붙여서 사용해주고 저장(cmd + s)을 해주면 <code class=\"language-text\">output.css</code> 에 해당 구문에 대한 <code class=\"language-text\">tailwind CSS</code> 가 추가된다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>❌  주의할 점 ❌ <br>\n아까 build 과정에서 <code class=\"language-text\">controll + c</code> 로 빠져나갔으면 적용이 안 될수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"bootstrap-with-tailwind","date":"August 25, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/PROJECT/bootstrap-with-tailwind/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/ERROR/spring-boot-test-error/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"스프링부트 테스트 에러"}},"next":null}}}